<item>
            <title>[LU-14878] replay-dual test_26: dbench 5354 missing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14878</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;adilger@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/68124ac2-6e83-47f3-9208-74b3bc90d970&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/68124ac2-6e83-47f3-9208-74b3bc90d970&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_26 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;4058.437544] Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: test_26 fail mds1 1 times
[ 4059.284890] LustreError: 11-0: lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff89b876701800: operation mds_reint to node 10.9.4.9@tcp failed: rc = -19
[ 4083.359933] LustreError: 10483:0:(client.c:3048:ptlrpc_replay_interpret()) @@@ status 301, old was 0  req@ffff89b863fc4900 x1705423006076800/t154618822711(154618822711) o101-&amp;gt;lustre-MDT0000-mdc-ffff89b8649a8800@10.9.4.9@tcp:12/10 lens 584/568 e 0 to 0 dl 1626422122 ref 2 fl Interpret:R/4/0 rc 301/301
[ 4083.365090] LustreError: 10483:0:(client.c:3048:ptlrpc_replay_interpret()) Skipped 2 previous similar messages
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This may of may not relate to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7372&quot; title=&quot;replay-dual test_26: test failed to respond and timed out&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7372&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7372&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. This subtest was disabled until 2021-06-11, but the actual problem was caused by test_25. However, the symptoms of this failure are quite different that &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7372&quot; title=&quot;replay-dual test_26: test failed to respond and timed out&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7372&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7372&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, so raising this as a separate ticket. &lt;/p&gt;





&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
replay-dual test_26 - dbench 5354 missing&lt;/p&gt;</description>
